# ============================================
# PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST
# ============================================
# Before deploying to production, verify:
# ✅ All passwords are strong, unique, and randomly generated
# ✅ JWT_SECRET is base64-encoded and at least 64 bytes (88+ chars after encoding)
